                    var l = this._lastTime = +new Date
                      , f = this._lastPos = this._draggable._absPos || this._draggable._newPos;
                    this._positions.push(f),
                    this._times.push(l),
                    this._prunePositions(l)
                }
                this._map.fire("move", o).fire("drag", o)
            },
            _prunePositions: function(o) {
                for (; this._positions.length > 1 && o - this._times[0] > 50; )
                    this._positions.shift(),
                    this._times.shift()
            },
            _onZoomEnd: function() {
                var o = this._map.getSize().divideBy(2)
                  , l = this._map.latLngToLayerPoint([0, 0]);
                this._initialWorldOffset = l.subtract(o).x,
                this._worldWidth = this._map.getPixelWorldBounds().getSize().x
            },
            _viscousLimit: function(o, l) {
                return o - (o - l) * this._viscosity
            },
            _onPreDragLimit: function() {
                if (!(!this._viscosity || !this._offsetLimit)) {

function NK() {

            }

                searchFilters: {

                    fromTime: n.searchFilters.fromTime ?? Aa.fromTime,
                    toTime: n.searchFilters.toTime ?? Aa.toTime,

                    date: r,

                },
                sortMode: i,
                viewMode: s
            }
        }
    } catch (t) {

    }

        searchFilters: Aa,
        sortMode: A1,
        viewMode: R1
    }
}
function PK() {

        t(d => ({
            ...d,
            viewMode: typeof u == "function" ? u(d.viewMode) : u
        }))
    }
    ;
    return {
        searchFilters: p.useMemo( () => e.searchFilters, [(a = e.searchFilters.date) == null ? void 0 : a.toISOString(), e.searchFilters.players, e.searchFilters.fromTime, e.searchFilters.toTime, e.searchFilters.holes, e.searchFilters.courseSearch, e.searchFilters.showFavoritesOnly]),
        setSearchFilters: n,
        sortMode: e.sortMode,
        setSortMode: r,
        viewMode: e.viewMode,
        setViewMode: i
    }
}
const bg = "/assets/Daytime_Costa_del_Sol_golf_walk_d48fdca9-B9fgjBZz.png"
  , EK = "/assets/golf%20video_1763551739293-CPkL9Q18.mp4";
function Qa(e) {
    return e.length === 0 ? null : Math.min(...e.map(t => t.greenFee))
}
function DK(e) {
    return e.length === 0 ? null : e.reduce( (t, n) => n.greenFee < t.greenFee ? n : t)
}
function MK(e) {
    const t = e.getHours();
    return t < 11 ? "morning" : t < 14 ? "midday" : t < 17 ? "afternoon" : "twilight"
}
function AK(e) {
    const t = {
        morning: [],
        midday: [],
        afternoon: [],
        twilight: []
    };
    return e.forEach(n => {
        const r = MK(new Date(n.teeTime));
        t[r].push(n)
    }
    ),
    Object.keys(t).forEach(n => {
        t[n].sort( (r, i) => new Date(r.teeTime).getTime() - new Date(i.teeTime).getTime())
    }
    ),
    t
}
function RK(e) {
    return e.length === 0 ? 0 : e.reduce( (t, n) => t + n.greenFee, 0) / e.length
}
function j1(e, t) {
    return t === 0 ? !1 : (t - e.greenFee) / t * 100 >= 15
}
function jK(e, t) {
    return t === 0 ? 0 : Math.round((t - e) / t * 100)
}
function IK(e) {
    return e == null ? "furtherAway" : e <= 15 ? "nearby" : e <= 40 ? "shortDrive" : "furtherAway"
}
function LK(e) {
    const t = {
        nearby: [],
        shortDrive: [],
        furtherAway: []
    };
    return e.forEach(n => {
        const r = IK(n.distanceKm);
        t[r].push(n)
    }
    ),
    Object.keys(t).forEach(n => {
        t[n].sort( (r, i) => (r.distanceKm ?? 1 / 0) - (i.distanceKm ?? 1 / 0))
    }
    ),
    t
}
function OK(e, t) {
    const n = [...e];
    switch (t) {
    case "distance-asc":
        return n.sort( (r, i) => {
            const s = r.distanceKm ?? 1 / 0
              , a = i.distanceKm ?? 1 / 0;
            return s - a
        }
        );
    case "distance-desc":
        return n.sort( (r, i) => {
            const s = r.distanceKm ?? -1 / 0;
            return (i.distanceKm ?? -1 / 0) - s
        }
        );
    case "price-asc":
        return n.sort( (r, i) => {
            const s = Qa(r.slots) ?? 1 / 0
              , a = Qa(i.slots) ?? 1 / 0;
            return s - a
        }
        );
    case "price-desc":
        return n.sort( (r, i) => {
            const s = Qa(r.slots) ?? -1 / 0;
            return (Qa(i.slots) ?? -1 / 0) - s
        }
        );
    default:
        return n
    }
}
